G \simeq \mathbb Z^r \oplus \bigoplus_{i=1}^m \mathbb Z / p_i^{a_i}
\mathrm{Hom}(G, \mathbb Z/p) \simeq \mathrm{Hom}(\mathbb Z, \mathbb Z/p)^r \oplus \bigoplus_{i=1}^m \mathrm{Hom}(\mathbb Z/p_i^{a_i}, \mathbb Z/p)
\mathrm{Hom}(H, \mathbb Z/p) \simeq \begin{cases} \mathbb Z/p & H = \mathbb Z \\ \mathbb Z/p & H = \mathbb Z/p^k \\ 0 & H = \mathbb Z/q^k \wedge q \neq p \end{cases}
r + |\{ i : p_i = p\}| = n
